fairytale : a true story is a 1997 french-american fantasy drama film directed by charles sturridge and produced by bruce davey and wendy &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it is loosely based on the story of the &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; fairies . its plot takes place in the year 1917 in england , and follows two children who take a photograph soon believed to be the first scientific evidence of the existence of fairies . the film was produced by icon productions and was distributed by paramount pictures in the united states and by warner bros. internationally ; it was released in the united states on october 24 , 1997 .